    <description>Combat Commander: Battle Pack #1 &amp;ndash; Paratroopers is the first of what will be many themed collections of scenarios for use with the Combat Commander: Europe series of games. The theme of this first Battle Pack is focused on the exploits of American, German and even Russian Airborne forces. CC&amp;ndash;Paratroopers features eleven new scenarios printed on cardstock, as well as four new maps. Future Battle Packs will be similarly structured and may also include new counters or new cards &amp;ndash; with themes such as &amp;ldquo;Stalingrad&amp;rdquo;, &amp;ldquo;Partisans&amp;rdquo; and &amp;ldquo;Desert Rats&amp;rdquo; to name just a few.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;COMPONENTS:&amp;#10;2 17&amp;quot; x 22&amp;quot; 2-sided color mapsheets&amp;#10;6 2-sided Scenario Cards&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The scenarios included in CC&amp;ndash;Paratroopers are:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;    &amp;ldquo;Fields of Fire&amp;rdquo; and &amp;ldquo;Fields of Blood&amp;rdquo; set at Lanzerath, Germany, 16 December 1944 &amp;ndash; both the morning and the afternoon attacks (using a new map #25);&amp;#10;    &amp;ldquo;Turnbull Turns &amp;lsquo;em&amp;rdquo; at Neuville-au-Plain, France, 6 June 1944 (using a new map #26);&amp;#10;    &amp;ldquo;Carentan Causeway&amp;rdquo; at Carentan, France, 10 June 1944 (using a new map #27);&amp;#10;    &amp;ldquo;No Ingouf Around&amp;rdquo; at Carentan, France, 11 June 1944 (using a new map #28);&amp;#10;    &amp;ldquo;Operation Repulse&amp;rdquo; at Bastogne, Belgium, 27 December 1944;&amp;#10;    &amp;ldquo;Red Skies at Night&amp;rdquo; at Veliki Bukrin Bridgehead, Russia, 25 September 1943;&amp;#10;    &amp;ldquo;Blizzard Baptism&amp;rdquo; at Flamierge, Belgium, 4 January 1945;&amp;#10;    &amp;ldquo;Look Mom, No Tanks!&amp;rdquo; near Trois Ponts, Belgium, 24 December 1944;&amp;#10;    &amp;ldquo;We Go!&amp;rdquo; at St. Mere Eglise, France, 6 June 1944;&amp;#10;    &amp;ldquo;Encircled at Hill 30&amp;rdquo; at Caponnet, France, 8 June 1944.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;NOTE: CC&amp;ndash;Paratroopers is not a complete game and requires ownership of Combat Commander: Europe to play.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Scenario designs in this first Pack are courtesy of Will Green, John Holme, Gregory L. Wong, Bryan Collars, Ric Van Dyke, Tray Green and Dan Holte.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
